Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.35,0:00:02.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,上一集的Love Live! Superstar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.94,0:00:04.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,为了迎接地区预赛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.15,0:00:05.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Liella!开始撰写新曲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.98,0:00:09.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然而我却被最近接触的游戏吸引…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.49,0:00:11.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,请不要告诉其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:12.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一旦这种事曝光的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:14.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.03,0:00:18.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,香音同学担心我 表示要当学生会副会长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:19.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想为你出一份力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:21.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,接受香音同学的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:23.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我坦白了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:27.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,与大家变得更加亲近后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:29.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我终于将新曲完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:31.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那么接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.72,0:00:34.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,开始举行新生学生会的创立典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:40.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,学生会书记 樱小路希奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:41.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.98,0:00:46.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,再来是会计 七草七海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.23,0:00:47.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.90,0:00:50.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是目前都没想过的新人选呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:52.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,为了学校好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:56.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,恋学姐说也要让音乐班以外的学生加入
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.07,0:00:57.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不愧是学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.07,0:00:59.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可可想当会计
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:00.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:02.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就多为社团出点力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:05.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,学生会长又离我更遥远了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:06.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你还没放弃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:09.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,学生会副会长 涩谷香音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:10.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:17.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,结丘女子高级中学学生会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:20.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,将加入新成员继续活动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:24.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明年将是齐聚三个年级的重要年度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:28.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,为此 本月将举行校园开放日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:31.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,让我们一同宣传本校的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:32.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,携手打造令在场各位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:36.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,都能感到骄傲的美好学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:48.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,来 奋战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:52.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,掀起我们的旋风
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:54.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,爬上巅峰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:55.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们绝不认输
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.93,0:01:57.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要拿下胜利!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:07.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不够 还不够 远远不够!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:10.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不论何时我都要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:13.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,超越昨天的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:16.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,究竟能走到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,虽然仍旧不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:18.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,还是要燃烧自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:21.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想与你一同欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:24.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想了解尚未知晓的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:27.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我还会更加成长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:29.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不想轻易放弃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:33.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,现在立刻 Start up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:38.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,向顶点前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:41.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,还要更加 更进一步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:44.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,更加情绪高昂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:47.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去实现吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:49.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在这瞬间 尽自己所能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:52.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,追寻梦想 尽自己全力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:57.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因为邂逅 给了我热情的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:03:00.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:04.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就算是不可能的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:05.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也去实现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:08.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们会继续相信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:11.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没错 WE WILL!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:21.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,像这个 这个 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,还有这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:25.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(#08 Chance Way)\N全都是Love Live!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:29.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是去年各校学园偶像使用过的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:32.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎么还在讲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:34.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,别擅自开灯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.32,0:03:35.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,天亮了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:36.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,居然睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:38.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Me too…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:42.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,意思是 舞台确实很重要咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:42.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:45.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今年地区预赛突然变成了远距大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:49.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因此在比去年多很多的参赛者中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:51.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们必须更吸引目光才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:54.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,比去年多啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.34,0:03:56.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有什么具体的点子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:04:00.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可可早就想到堇会问这种不经大脑的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:03.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以已经准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:05.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:09.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,包下外苑球场计划!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:12.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:13.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在球场中央搭建舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:20.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,从360度各种角度来进行Liella!的直播
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:22.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:25.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你之前不是才被回绝过一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:28.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,CP值也是低到不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:31.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没问题的 我们可是当地的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:33.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而且还是优胜候补
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:34.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,身为学园偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.09,0:04:39.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎么可以还没尝试就先放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你能明白我的想法吗…!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:42.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那当然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:45.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要努力就一定能办到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:46.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,拥有不放弃的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:50.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,才正是学园偶像!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:51.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,对哒! 对哒!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:52.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:54.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,失败了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:56.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,被骂得好惨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那不是当然的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:00.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:02.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你们两个意外地像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:06.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不过这样该选哪里好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:08.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这种时候比起浪费钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:12.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,更应该思考有效果的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:13.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有效果的?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:15.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有什么好意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:17.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你们好好想一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:20.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,赢家是由观众进行人气投票选出
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:21.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:24.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,重点是如何引起观众的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:26.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这大家都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:28.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,问题是方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:29.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:32.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,比方说 投票给Liella!的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.98,0:05:36.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,都能获得在场成员的密藏照片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:39.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然后追加斗内money的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:40.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,竟然还…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:41.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.78,0:05:44.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我都还没说要干嘛欸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:45.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:47.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只能靠大家集思广益找出答案了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:49.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,找出能充分传达Liella! 结丘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:53.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,以及我们几个的象征的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:55.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,象征…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:01.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,说是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:02.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,实在是想不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:04.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,结丘的象征吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:07.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,例如说到雪国的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:09.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就有下雪的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:12.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,学校在海边的话就是大海之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:15.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,结丘附近也有很多知名景点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:18.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有很大条的路 还有店家…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:22.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不过那些能算是结丘的特色吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:23.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:26.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因为太有名了 感觉无法代表结丘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:27.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这是?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:31.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是各社团的校园开放日企划书哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:32.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,居然有这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:35.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这表示大家很重视这所学校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:39.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想大家都越来越喜欢学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:45.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,学园偶像社这次打算做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:48.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,完全忘记了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:50.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,果然还是举办演唱会…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我正打算提这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:55.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这次不办演唱会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:06:58.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,学生会已经讨论过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:01.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要让我们专心准备地区预赛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:02.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:03.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:07.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只不过多一场演唱会 可可完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我本来也是这样说的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:11.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那又怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:14.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小七海是说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:15.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如果办演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:19.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,会不会大家就都只注意Liella!了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:21.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:23.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,毕竟学园祭也办过演唱会了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:25.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,考虑整所学校的发展
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:28.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这次就让其他社团来炒热气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:30.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,或许才更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:33.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那我们要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:36.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不办演唱会唱歌的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:38.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(结丘女子 校园开放日)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:46.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:49.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小千的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:52.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,NEO彩虹章鱼烧烤好咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:56.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:57.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,完全没人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:08:00.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真奇怪 明明这么圆的说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:02.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我觉得问题不在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:02.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,颜色…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:05.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,危机就是转机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如果不预测流行趋势
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:10.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Money可是不会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:11.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:15.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,用上这杯为了章鱼烧特制的高人气冰沙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:17.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟章鱼烧混合起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:20.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是彩虹章鱼烧冰沙咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:21.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Pass
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:22.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这是要怎么吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:24.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:27.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,先将这根特制的吸管插入杯中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:29.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,再一口气…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:34.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喉咙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:37.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,直接烫到喉咙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:38.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:41.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:44.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这里看起没问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:46.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,希奈子学妹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:49.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可以麻烦你去帮忙音乐班的话剧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:50.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,校园开放日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:56.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这么多人来真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,"虽然学生人数少"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:09:00.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,"但是更有团结力 是所好学校"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,之前杂志也这么介绍了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:07.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,逐渐成为你妈妈理想中的学校了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:11.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:13.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,亚里亚? 你今天有来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:16.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想给姐姐一个惊喜嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:18.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,再说我也得决定要念哪所学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:21.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这样的话我可以带你参观啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:24.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明年请务必考虑加入学园偶像社
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等等 小可可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:28.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,姐妹一起当学园偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:29.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是很热血的展开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:30.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:33.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我甚至还没决定要不要报考结丘耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:36.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:38.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:39.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:43.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有好多书
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.73,0:09:47.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原来香音妹妹对书有兴趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:48.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她这点很像我爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:52.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,放假时总是在读书
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:55.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,虽然是姐妹但是兴趣不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:57.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:10:01.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这里原本是音乐学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:04.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,为什么会想在这个地方建立学校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:05.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:09.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,会选这个地点的理由 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:14.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(章鱼烧冰沙~)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:16.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎么办啦 剩这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:17.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,果然冰沙根本就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:19.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,学姐在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:22.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是章鱼烧的问题啦 章鱼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:24.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,才不是 圆形是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:26.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟圆形没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:28.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,越讲越复杂了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:29.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎样都好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:31.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,意外地…不错吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:32.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的假的!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:37.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,音乐学校的历史…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:39.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:40.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:41.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,对了 要收拾才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:43.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,已经结束咯 给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:46.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:48.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,卖剩的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你在调查这座城市的历史吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:55.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想说这所学校为什么会建在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:58.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,或许能成为决定舞台地点的线索…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.68,0:10:59.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那你找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:02.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可惜还没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:04.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(您有新信息 悠奈)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:05.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,日团?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:07.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,舞台?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:09.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,机会难得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:11.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们想让最信任的学园偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:13.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,先看看我们的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:15.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这可是我们的自信之作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:16.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,日团大人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:17.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,舞台…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:19.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这会爆红
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:21.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就让我先发到网络上…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:23.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,信任关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:28.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那么 这就是国内首次公开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:31.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Sunny Passion今年的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:37.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,多么美妙的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:39.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好想到现场看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:41.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这是岛上的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:44.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,以我们为形象准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:45.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,毕竟是最后一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:46.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,最后?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:51.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就算我们能突破地区预赛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:54.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,接着的东京大赛 还有后面的决赛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:11:59.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很高概率会选东京的大舞台来当会场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:01.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这么一来 我们能在这座岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:05.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,以学园偶像身份站上舞台的机会就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:10.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因为与这座岛屿共存
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:12.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,还有伙伴们的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:13.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们才能走到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:15.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们想跟这所学校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.09,0:12:17.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一起让岛上变得更加热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:20.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,希望大家都能来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:24.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,让我们都办场美好的演唱会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:25.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:27.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:30.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们也得赶快找到才行…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:35.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:40.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:43.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今天明明礼拜天 你也很早起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:44.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要去练习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:47.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在那之前我想散步一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:48.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,散步?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:53.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妈妈你最喜欢这座城市的什么地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:03.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,5 6 7 8…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:06.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小希奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:09.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,咦 香音学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:14.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎么了 学姐也在自行练习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:15.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:19.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今天我想找找选择舞台的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:23.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,对了 小希奈子是今年才来这里的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:24.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有空的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:27.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要不要跟我一起去街上逛逛?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:28.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟香音学姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:31.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:33.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要去要去!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:40.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟香音学姐一起逛街
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:42.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:43.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沾到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:49.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,话说回来 从早上就好多人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:51.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,毕竟是假日 所以更多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:54.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是常常在电视上看到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好多时髦的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:59.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在拍戏耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:00.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那里也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:01.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这里也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:03.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,到处都是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:06.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:08.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:10.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,无论到哪都很热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:11.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家都笑咪咪的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.54,0:14:15.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,希奈子是在人烟稀少的地方长大的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:17.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以光是这样就觉得很兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:22.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,香音学姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:24.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,到处都很热闹…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:26.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,人潮聚集的城市…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:27.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,香音学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:29.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:32.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,学姐是不是找到什么线索了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:37.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,感觉…已经到这里了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:44.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小香音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:46.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你们来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:50.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,之后就交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:52.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,请问是怎么一回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:54.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,到Love Live结束前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:56.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小香音你们就专心练习
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:57.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这段期间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:15:00.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,学生会的工作就交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:03.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们去年也有帮忙搭舞台啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这让我们很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:07.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但要是打进全国大赛的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:10.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,时间就会拉得很长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:12.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要麻烦你们这么久实在…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:16.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们也想跟你们分享喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:18.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以有什么我们能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:20.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,能帮忙的我们全都想做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:22.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,为了不留下任何遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:30.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要哭还太早了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:33.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,千砂都你自己还不是哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:38.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,毕竟她是爱哭鬼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:41.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嘴上这么说 堇学姐也在哭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:44.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是太谢谢你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:55.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,来 1 2 3 4 5 6 7…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:58.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,奇怪 数字怎样都对不上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:00.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,从头算看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:02.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,为什么对不上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:03.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原来叶月同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一直都在做这么辛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:09.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好好感受自己的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:11.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我 我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:16.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:20.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我很擅长静止不动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:21.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(Liella! 舞台会议!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:26.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,现在开始Liella!舞台会议
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:29.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有任何点子的请尽管举手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:30.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:36.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,还有这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:38.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这是舞台地点的候补名单
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是七海同学她们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:42.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,向校内同学做问卷调查的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:43.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟预料的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:45.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很多人选表参道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:49.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,毕竟这条路从100多年前就在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:51.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,果然比较引人注目
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:54.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但我们去年就是在这里唱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:57.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,的确也能刻意选同个地点…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:17:00.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但就缺乏冲击力了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:01.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一大难题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:02.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:06.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:10.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,学校的大家是在这里为我们搭建舞台的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:16.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家肯定是觉得这里很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:21.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,表参道…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:24.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,道路…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:27.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,刚才的名单里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:31.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,还有一个…还有一个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:34.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小香音?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:45.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:48.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,既热闹 人潮又多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,从很久以前就在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:08.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,串起大家想法 属于我们的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:13.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小香音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:15.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跑太快了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:18.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我问你怎样就到底是怎样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:20.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你们…怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:22.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不管是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:25.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看到你那样突然冲出去都会很在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:26.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,到底发生什么事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:28.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:32.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我好像找到我们的舞台了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:35.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:36.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:38.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:39.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:40.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这里是…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:42.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,道路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:46.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们的学校会建在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:48.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,会不会是因为这里是道路交会的场所呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:51.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,道路…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:55.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因为这里是道路交会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:57.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,集结了人们的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:19:00.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是集结了每个人的梦想与希望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:02.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,彼此连结的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:14.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以我们才会选择在这里搭建舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:19.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,人与人之间互相连结 产生连系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:22.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,结丘就是这样的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:25.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在这个道路交会的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:28.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们要献上歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:38.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,希望Liella!的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:40.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,结丘的道路…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:45.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,能与你产生交集
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:10.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,追逐梦想也没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.19,0:20:11.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,尽情喧闹也没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:12.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:13.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我不在乎 无论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:15.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,试着倾听自己内心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:17.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如果不自由地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:18.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,尝试所有事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:19.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就太可惜了! Jump吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:20.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Every time 都是祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:22.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,鼓起勇气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:23.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,快点靠过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:24.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:26.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,肆意喧闹吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:27.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,往心跳的另一头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:28.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,准备好就一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:29.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这样不是很好吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:33.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,连上衣都想脱掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:35.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Yeah! 尽情享受吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:41.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没错! 我想更加了解你的事!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:45.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,相遇之日正是 Chance Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:49.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,命运绝非偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:53.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一同起舞吧 改变世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:55.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(全都变得Colorful)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:59.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,心情交织叠成 Chance Way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:02.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,活力彼此连结
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:08.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,来做一件 最厉害的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:15.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,放声歌唱 一起欢笑玩耍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:25.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,祭典开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.39,0:21:29.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,合而为一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:31.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:51.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们是结丘女子学园偶像社
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:54.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.01,0:22:05.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(结丘女子学园偶像)\N(Liella! 晋级东京大赛!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.97,0:22:12.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在我追逐的梦想前方 总是能看见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:15.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,名为希望的星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.89,0:22:20.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,正在闪烁着 闪烁耀眼光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.56,0:22:23.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,即便跌倒也能再次前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.19,0:22:28.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在我追逐的梦想前方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:33.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我究竟会走向何处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:38.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,场场相遇之中 虽然又会迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.96,0:22:42.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,请试着去享受这一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.46,0:22:45.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,觉得「似乎能做到却做不到」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:47.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,最后做到的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:50.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就会很开心 想着要好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:54.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,整颗心都像是要跳了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:22:59.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,尽情欢笑 放声高歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:01.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.40,0:23:05.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,继续走向远方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:07.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,世界广阔无边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:10.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,虽然也有景色会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:13.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但热情会始终如一!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:17.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跨越许多后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:19.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想实现的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.50,0:23:23.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,来吧 大家一起去实现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.50,0:23:28.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明天要弹奏出什么样的悸动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:32.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去改变未来吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:39.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,下集 为了胜利
